data.description: Welcome to an exciting opportunity for investors! This ranch, located on a quiet cul-de-sac road, with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, this property is poised for a revival. Whether you're a seasoned investor or a DIY enthusiast, envision the possibilities as you breathe new life into this residence. Step into the expansive living room, featuring a brick gas fireplace that adds warmth and character. French doors open seamlessly to the backyard, creating a harmonious indoor-outdoor flow. The kitchen boasts a convenient bar top, perfect for casual meals, and is complemented by a separate dining room for more formal gatherings. The two-car garage comes complete with a utility room/workshop. Conveniently located near Atlanta Hwy, the Athens loop and UGA. Only minutes away from dining and shopping. This property is being sold AS-IS and is priced accordingly.
